title: 'Product is as expected!'
body: I would like to recommend this BATA Men's slipper. I initially thought this would be a simple slipper while ordering and I would manage with this for 2-3 months and will find new one. But once upon receiving, I found the quality as I expected and the blue color is slipper is looking awesome.  Overall, I am very much happy with the product in terms of quality and the amount they charged.
